summary: No context | 08.11.18
title: No context | 08.11.18
body:
Phil: This is a lot of stuff to be in my mouth. Right now. I think I need to spit it out or be quiet for a while.
Dan: ...
Phil: Erm... You started nice- I'm just going to spit it out.
Dan: I'm not going to say- I... Wow.
*Phil gets up and leaves for a moment*
Dan: I apologise. I'm really, really upset.
Phil *off-screen*: Ugh. This is gross. 
Dan: ...
Phil: I was going to say-
Dan: That entire 30 seconds happened. What was I saying?
